<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Terms of Use — DUBIMOTORS</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css" />
  <style>
    .legal-hero { background: var(--dark); padding: 56px 0 40px; }
    .legal-hero-title { font-size: 36px; font-weight: 900; color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .legal-hero-sub { font-size: 14px; color: #666; }
    .legal-body { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 56px 0 80px; }
    .legal-body h2 { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 900; color: var(--dark); margin: 36px 0 12px; }
    .legal-body p { font-size: 14px; color: #555; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .legal-body ul { padding-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .legal-body ul li { font-size: 14px; color: #555; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .legal-updated { display: inline-block; background: rgba(232,69,10,0.1); color: var(--orange); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 20px; margin-bottom: 32px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div id="navbar-placeholder"></div>

<div class="legal-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="legal-hero-title">Terms of Use</div>
    <div class="legal-hero-sub">The rules and conditions governing your use of the DUBIMOTORS platform.</div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container">
  <div class="legal-body">
    <div class="legal-updated">Last updated: 1 March 2025</div>

    <p>These Terms of Use ("Terms") govern your access to and use of the DUBIMOTORS website, mobile applications, and services (collectively, the "Platform"). By accessing or using the Platform, you agree to be bound by these Terms. If you do not agree, please do not use the Platform.</p>

    <h2>1. Eligibility</h2>
    <p>You must be at least 18 years of age to use the Platform. By using the Platform, you represent and warrant that you meet this requirement and that you have the legal capacity to enter into a binding agreement.</p>

    <h2>2. Account Registration</h2>
    <p>To access certain features, you must create an account. You agree to provide accurate, current, and complete information during registration and to keep your account information updated. You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your password and for all activity that occurs under your account. You must notify us immediately of any unauthorised use of your account.</p>

    <h2>3. Listing Rules</h2>
    <p>When placing an advertisement on the Platform, you agree that:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>You are the legal owner of the vehicle or are authorised to sell it on behalf of the owner.</li>
      <li>All information provided in the listing is accurate, complete, and not misleading.</li>
      <li>Photos used are genuine photos of the actual vehicle being sold.</li>
      <li>The asking price is genuine and you intend to sell at or near that price.</li>
      <li>You will not post duplicate listings for the same vehicle.</li>
      <li>You will not post listings for vehicles that are stolen, have outstanding finance, or have a salvage title without clear disclosure.</li>
      <li>You will remove the listing promptly once the vehicle is sold.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>4. Prohibited Conduct</h2>
    <p>You agree not to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Use the Platform for any unlawful purpose or in violation of UAE law.</li>
      <li>Post false, misleading, or fraudulent listings or information.</li>
      <li>Harass, threaten, or abuse other users.</li>
      <li>Attempt to circumvent any security measures or access controls.</li>
      <li>Use automated tools, bots, or scrapers to access or collect data from the Platform without our written consent.</li>
      <li>Impersonate any person or entity or misrepresent your affiliation with any person or entity.</li>
      <li>Post content that infringes the intellectual property rights of any third party.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>5. Fees and Payments</h2>
    <p>Basic listings are free. Featured and Premium listing packages are subject to fees as displayed on the Platform at the time of purchase. All fees are in UAE Dirhams (AED) and are non-refundable unless otherwise stated. We reserve the right to change our fee structure at any time with reasonable notice.</p>

    <h2>6. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
    <p>The Platform is provided "as is" and "as available" without warranties of any kind, either express or implied. DUBIMOTORS does not warrant that the Platform will be uninterrupted, error-free, or free of viruses. We do not verify the accuracy of listings posted by users and are not responsible for any transactions between buyers and sellers.</p>

    <h2>7. Limitation of Liability</h2>
    <p>To the maximum extent permitted by UAE law, DUBIMOTORS shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages arising from your use of the Platform or any transaction conducted through the Platform. Our total liability to you for any claim shall not exceed the amount you paid us in the 12 months preceding the claim.</p>

    <h2>8. Intellectual Property</h2>
    <p>All content on the Platform, including but not limited to the DUBIMOTORS name, logo, design, text, graphics, and software, is owned by or licensed to DUBIMOTORS and is protected by UAE and international intellectual property laws. You may not reproduce, distribute, or create derivative works from any Platform content without our written consent.</p>

    <h2>9. Termination</h2>
    <p>We reserve the right to suspend or terminate your account and access to the Platform at any time, with or without notice, for conduct that we determine violates these Terms, is harmful to other users, or is otherwise objectionable. You may terminate your account at any time by contacting us.</p>

    <h2>10. Governing Law</h2>
    <p>These Terms shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the United Arab Emirates. Any disputes arising from these Terms or your use of the Platform shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts of Dubai, UAE.</p>

    <h2>11. Changes to These Terms</h2>
    <p>We may update these Terms from time to time. We will notify you of material changes by posting a notice on the Platform or sending you an email. Your continued use of the Platform after changes are posted constitutes your acceptance of the updated Terms.</p>

    <h2>12. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions about these Terms, please contact us at:<br>
    <strong>DUBIMOTORS</strong><br>
    Email: legal@dubimotors.ae<br>
    Address: Dubai, United Arab Emirates</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="footer-placeholder"></div>
<script src="shared.js"></script>
<script src="components.js"></script>
<script>renderNavbar(); renderFooter();</script>
</body>
</html>
